<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 13:16:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>有数百万种加密代币。几乎没有任何价值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-06/there-are-millions-of-crypto-tokens-almost-none-have-any-value</link><description>查尔斯·霍斯金森很生气。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikEKVt3kcQkU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-06/there-are-millions-of-crypto-tokens-almost-none-have-any-value</guid></item><item><title>自 2024 年特朗普获胜以来，比特币首次跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-falls-below-60-000-for-first-time-since-2024-trump-win</link><description>比特币自 2024 年 10 月以来首次跌破 60,000 美元，从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普连任后的市场宠儿转变为快速变化的投机格局的牺牲品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iut13rHAsVz0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 16:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-falls-below-60-000-for-first-time-since-2024-trump-win</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院主要委员会正在准备立法以制定加密货币税收结构</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</link><description>负责税收政策的众议院小组正在准备立法，赋予加密货币持有者在报告投资收益方面更大的灵活性，这对数字资产行业来说是一个潜在的福音。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQWwstahc5G8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 23:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币接近特朗普之前的低点，加密货币暴跌加剧</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</link><description>比特币周五下跌多达 5%，因为这种原始加密货币面临一波持续的抛售压力，接近美国总统唐纳德·特朗普赢得连任之前以来的最低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJcA.uTjm7M8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 07:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</guid></item></channel></rss>